" 'No, I have not. It mustbe those wretched gipsies in theplantation.'

"'Very likely. And yet if it were on the lawn, Iwonder that youdid not hear italso.'

" 'Ah,but I sleep moreheavily than you.'

" 'Well, itis of no greatconsequence, atany rate.' She smiled back at me, closed my door, and a few moments later I heard her key turn in the lock."

