"I wasrecalled to myself by a franticplucking at mywrist, and I found myself lyingupon the stone floor of a narrowcorridor, whilea woman bent over me and tuggedat me with herleft hand, whileshe held a candle in her right.It was the samegood friend whose warning I hadso foolishly rejected.

