" 'Quite sure, dad.'" 'Then, good-night.' I kissedher and went upto my bedroom again, where I wassoon asleep.

"I am endeavouring to tell you everything, Mr. Holmes, which mayhave any bearingupon the case,but I beg that you will questionme upon any point which I do not make clear.""On the contrary, your statementis singularly lucid."

